Apex Music v4.56

==What's New==
=What's Been Added=
-Nothing has been added

=What's Been Removed=
-Persistent notification option

=What's Been Changed & Updated=
-ID3 and synced lyrics will now disable when the lyrics type option is set to disabled
-Navigation bar color on player themes
-Classic player theme layout

=What's Planned To Be Removed/Changed=
-Audio fade and crossfade options need to be fixed as they cause headset controls to be unresponsive

==What's Fixed==
-Big widget crash when clearing playing queue

==Possible Bugs==
-Audio fade and crossfade options causes headset controls to be unresponsive. use these options with caution
-When using the peek now playing theme on tablets or foldables the navigation side rail may disappear completely. this should be automatically fixed when collapsing the mini player
-Some android skins such as funtouch os may experience issues with apex
-Material you may not work correctly on some android skins like oneui, due to the implementation method of material you into the android skin
-If you are experiencing any bugs, try reinstalling the app